markets.title: Will another LLM be better than Grok 3 before Apr 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If Grok 3 is the model with the highest Arena Elo Score after Issuance and before Apr 1, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: If there is any day where another model has a higher score than Grok 3, as checked at 10:00 AM ET, then the market immediately resolves to No. For the purposes of this contract, the "Grok 3" market refers to any model that is Grok 3. So if xAI releases a version of Grok 3 called "caramel" and it beats "chocolate", it would not count as Grok 3 being usurped as the top LLM.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
